Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Middle Markets is pleased to offer 8 & 10 Cato Street, Hawthorn East for sale.

8 Cato Street comprises of a modern commanding Corporate Office Headquarters, offering high quality office accommodation which is further supplemented by high clearance temperature-controlled warehouse at the rear. In addition to this the property benefits from an additional land parcel at 10 Cato Street, which provides 1,124sqm of land with future development potential (currently at-grade parking). 

Key benefits of this outstanding offering include:
+  Commanding corporate headquarters comprising 2,717sqm* of office and 937sqm* of warehouse
+  105* secure basement car parks (8 Cato) and 35 on grade car parks (10 Cato)
+  Substantial land holding of 3,371sqm over two separate titles
+  Vast combined frontage of over 59 metres* to Cato Street with rear access from Cato Lane
+  Flexible Commercial 2 zone, with potential to develop up to six (6) levels (STCA)
+  Offered with short term holding income*

Situated in the popular Hawthorn office market, the property occupies a prominent location seconds from the Monash Freeway and within walking distance to Tooronga Village Shopping Centre and Tooronga Train Station.

8 Cato Street is offered for sale with 10 Cato Street. The properties available to be purchased together or separately. 

10 Cato Street: www.realcommercial.com.au/for-sale/property-10-cato-street-hawthorn-east-vic-3123-503817090

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact one of the exclusive marketing agents.

*approximate
